Sentece: The fetal-maternal plasma accumulation ratio of 1.6:1 indicates that at this gestational age after 26 days of therapy, the placental transfer of phenoxybenzamine occurs and is accompanied by accumulation in the fetal blood.
Title: Phenoxybenzamine placental transfer during the third trimester.
Name: Phenoxybenzamine
